description: Manu Dibango, the 86-year-old African jazz legend, dies in Paris after catching the coronavirus.
title: Manu Dibango: African saxophone legend dies of Covid-19
title_page: Manu Dibango: African saxophone legend dies of Covid-19 - BBC News
maintext: Speaking to the BBC in 2013 about how he wanted to be remembered, Dibango said: "When you are gone, it is finished, it is not up to me to say, 'I want this.'"
